  "detailed_description": "<strong> Laser Grid is a first-person puzzle game in which you power devices by redirecting, combining and splitting different colored lasers. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/becffefcdf961d889435b1ae228b99f9.avif?t=1502836493\" width=600 height=68 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/28ab0d1be051cedaaab3a9fa14c1b91f.poster.avif?t=1502836493\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/28ab0d1be051cedaaab3a9fa14c1b91f.webm?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/28ab0d1be051cedaaab3a9fa14c1b91f.mp4?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> 32 mind bending puzzle rooms to master with 10+ hours of gameplay.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/cdf07e91880bd4fdb1d8cdc9e383cca9.poster.avif?t=1502836493\" width=576 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/cdf07e91880bd4fdb1d8cdc9e383cca9.webm?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/cdf07e91880bd4fdb1d8cdc9e383cca9.mp4?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>  Control lasers with a wide variety of different cube types such as glass, magnet, diffraction, laser, and Fresnel.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/92a565167a815b94f6ba9b89f49de873.poster.avif?t=1502836493\" width=576 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/92a565167a815b94f6ba9b89f49de873.webm?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/92a565167a815b94f6ba9b89f49de873.mp4?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>  New puzzle mechanics and cube types are introduced regularly which add complexity and difficulty.  You can also rotate the entire room to solve puzzles on the walls and ceiling. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/9df56af19c1971436284a79f7f180432.poster.avif?t=1502836493\" width=576 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/9df56af19c1971436284a79f7f180432.webm?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/9df56af19c1971436284a79f7f180432.mp4?t=1502836493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>  Laser Grid is available for PC and Mac! \t</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/613050/extras/6f75b8438357b2c292fbc3e2d99029ac.avif?t=1502836493\" width=323 height=95 /></span>",
